No, I'm not pissed at cops for being cops, I dont think I'm special and that the laws dont apply to me. Lots of people here took this the wrong way. I simply asked cops to think about what they are doing to the person they are busting. I can't count the amount of times I've thought about trying to become a cop so I could do it different. <br>
<br>
One of the few cops I respect has mine because he said &quot;I've never written a DWI. I've never issued a drug citation. I've never given a speeding ticket. Because of al the @#%$ up things that go on in this world, why should I be spending my time and joe shmoe's time with something that will end up in paper work for me, bills for him, and the feeling that cops are there to screw you. I have better things to do with my time, like busting people that actually need it.&quot;<br>
